    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A trademark for a two-part epoxy adhesive made with the diglycidyl ether of bisphenol A and triethylene diamine. Hxtal NYL-1 is a low viscosity, colorless, transparent resin that hardens to form a clearstrong bond. It has been used for glass and china repair. Hxtal may discolor in direct sunlight.</Note_Text>
